{"name": "odoo-addon-account-invoice-constraint-chronology", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-account-invoice-constraint-chronology", "version": "16.0.1.1.1", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 16.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/account-financial-tools", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "Account Invoice Constraint Chronology", "upload_time": 1734957471}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Faccount--financial--tools-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/account-financial-tools\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/account-financial-tools/tree/16.0/account_invoice_constraint_chronology\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/account-financial-tools-16-0/account-financial-tools-16-0-account_invoice_constraint_chronology\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/account-financial-tools&target_branch=16.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Account Invoice Constraint Chronology\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:2bbbbae5add4e2515f46564aec694f0c036512b69064d9334f748045b82478f4\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module helps ensuring the chronology of invoice numbers.\n\nIt prevents the validation of invoices when:\n\n- there are draft invoices with a prior date\n- there are validated invoices with a later date\n- there are validated invoices with a higher number\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/account-financial-tools/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/account-financial-tools/issues/new?body=module:%20account_invoice_constraint_chronology%0Aversion:%2016.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- ACSONE SA/NV\n- CorporateHub\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Adrien Peiffer ([Acsone SA/NV](http://www.acsone.eu))\n\n- Gilles Gilles \\<<mailto:meyomesse.gilles@gmail.com>>\n\n- Francesco Apruzzese \\<<mailto:f.apruzzese@apuliasoftware.it>>\n\n- Thomas Binsfeld \\<<mailto:thomas.binsfeld@acsone.eu>>\n\n- Souheil Bejaoui \\<<mailto:souheil.bejaoui@acsone.eu>>\n\n- [CorporateHub](https://corporatehub.eu/)\n\n  - Alexey Pelykh \\<<mailto:alexey.pelykh@corphub.eu>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/account-financial-tools](https://github.com/OCA/account-financial-tools/tree/16.0/account_invoice_constraint_chronology) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_constraint_chronology.tests", "documentation": ["License AGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_constraint_chronology.tests.test_account_invoice_constraint_chronology", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_constraint_chronology.tests..test_account_invoice_constraint_chronology", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_constraint_chronology", "documentation": ["License AGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_constraint_chronology.model", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_constraint_chronology..model", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_constraint_chronology.model.account_journal", "documentation": ["Copyright 2015-2019 ACSONE SA/NV (<http://acsone.eu>)", "Copyright 2021 CorporateHub (https://corporatehub.eu)", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl.html)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_constraint_chronology.model.account_journal.AccountJournal", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_constraint_chronology.model.account_journal.AccountJournal._onchange_type", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_invoice_constraint_chronology.model.account_journal.AccountJour